item.description:
## Media events

Apart from the HTTP API calls there are [Pusher](https://pusher.com) events with info about content. Since the media module relies on events being sent from pusher you must subscribe to the pusher-channel provided in the response of the [Get Target](#5810f0fe-7be7-6839-c4a7-307b2527777e) (pusher connection info) and [Get Stream](#aaa9244a-d56c-b2da-67df-3b63c36ae2b3) (the interaction channel id) calls.

## Content add

Channel: stream-{streamId}-media

Event: content-add

```
